%% 3.2.7 Edit Bus (Vehicle) — sequence (layered)

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Actor as Admin
    participant UI as UI (/vehicles)
    participant BC as Controller (BusController)
    participant BS as Service (BusService)
    participant Repo as Repository (IRepository Bus)
    participant DB as Database (SQL Server)

    UI->>BC: GET /api/Bus/Get/{id}
    BC-->>UI: BusDto

    Actor->>UI: Change capacity, status, driver selection UI
    alt Capacity invalid FE
        UI-->>Actor: Inline positive number
    else PUT
        UI->>BC: PUT /api/Bus/Update/{id} BusUpdateDto
        BC->>BS: UpdateBusAsync — ValidateCapacity greater than 0
        BS->>Repo: UPDATE
        Repo->>DB: UPDATE Buses
        BC-->>UI: 200
    end

    Note over UI,DB: Reassign driver — cập nhật BusAssignment / schedule nếu nghiệp vụ yêu cầu.
